{"tid":417582,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"習慣單身 已經turn off左？","createTime":"2017-09-28T20:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T06:22:14.000Z","uid":13531,"like":67,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"cc33aeba07c80008507a03ccbb2da157e8383917","tid":417582,"uid":13531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T20:18:20.000Z","msg":"細佬我依家讀緊yr3 距離上一段關係已經3年有多<br />\n<br />\n依段時間有好多女仔埋身 或者都有機會發展既 <br />\n<br />\n但都好似無咩興趣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到有一個真係有興趣想發展既<br />\n<br />\n但曖昧完一排又無咩下文 直到最近發現佢都有男朋友了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人問我係咪已經turn off左自己 咁耐都唔搵下一個<br />\n<br />\n因為上一段感情付出左好多 但結果都係不歡而散 <br />\n<br />\n我又唔想為拍拖而拍拖 求其搵個就算<br />\n<br />\n想搵個真係可以長久自己又鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好難遇到"},{"pid":"27e99fb4b84eb9d9c3f411b4091015b230259ab2","tid":417582,"uid":137847,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T20:38:38.000Z","msg":"哇一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論同幾多個人傾都好都冇一個及佢<br />\n都唔想再為出pool而出<br />\n一定好快散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251d66681a4c4903291fdb9f496b0a1d157f0339","tid":417582,"uid":13531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T20:39:09.000Z","msg":"毒撚開post無人理:<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3a366ee075bad664911d146ca4cf1a4f4c93eb","tid":417582,"uid":127012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T20:41:21.000Z","msg":"加油..."},{"pid":"0e00c003b430b0be6a9744f80d05e82a9b17ec8b","tid":417582,"uid":13531,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T20:45:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哇一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論同幾多個人傾都好都冇一個及佢<br />\n都唔想再為出pool而出<br />\n一定好快散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fro